    <string name="simple_chat_title">💬 Simple Chat</string>
    <string name="simple_chat_content">This is a simple chat interface for experimenting with unmodified models.
You can test their responses and performance directly without any additional processing.

Use any model with 📝 tag for writing capabilities.

> This is a direct conversation with the AI model as it was trained.
> Perfect for testing model capabilities and getting raw responses.</string>
    <string name="agent_title">🤖 I'm Llema, your personal assistant</string>
    <string name="agent_features_content">Features:

📝 Notes: Search, read, and create personal notes with tags

📅 Calendar: List events, find availability, and create new events

✅ Tasks: List and complete your tasks

👥 Contacts: Look up people by name, email, or phone

📍 Places: Find nearby restaurants, coffee shops, and more

⏰ Time: Get current time and calculate date offsets

> I am very small, I might not be as skilled as my bigger brothers, but I try my best.
> Sometimes you need to be more specific on what I should do.
> Use models with 🔧 tag for best agent experience.
> I can communicate in multiple languages but for best results use **English**.</string>
    
